 Information." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Cometriq (cabozantinib)." Exelixis Inc, S San Francisco, CA.[4] "Product Information. Sporanox (itraconazole)." Janssen Pharmaceutica, Titusville, NJ.[5] Wohlt PD, Zheng L, Gunderson S, Balzar SA, Johnson BD, Fish JT "Recommendations for the use of medications with continuous enteral nutrition." Am J Health Syst Pharm 66 (2009): 1438-67[6] "Product Information. VFEND (voriconazole)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[7] "Product Information. Cometriq (cabozantinib)." Exelixis Inc, S San Francisco, CA.', 1767365204);
